---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Computer Repair Services | Jake Fixes Tech — Littleton, NH"
description="Screen repair, virus removal, data recovery, hardware upgrades, gaming console repair and more. Flat rate pricing, no hidden fees. Serving Littleton NH.">

  <!-- Header Banner -->
  <section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;background-color:rgb(30,64,175);">
    <img src="/hero.jpg" alt="Professional tech workspace with dual monitors" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;z-index:0;" />
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(30,64,175,0.88),rgba(37,99,235,0.88));z-index:1;"></div>
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;position:relative;z-index:2;">
      <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#93c5fd;">What I Do</p>
      <h1 style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:white;line-height:1.2;">Services</h1>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;color:#bfdbfe;line-height:1.75;font-size:1.1rem;max-width:42rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        From quick software fixes to full hardware overhauls, I handle a wide range of tech repairs and services. No job is too big or too small.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Computer Repair -->
  <section style="background:#f8fafc;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">Computer Repair</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.25rem;">Hardware & Software Repairs</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.6;">Every repair backed by a 30 day labor warranty. Windows, Linux and Mac software supported.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <a id="screen-repair" href="/services/screen-repair" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Screen Repair</h3>
          <p>Cracked, flickering, or dead screens? I replace a variety of laptop and desktop screens quickly and affordably. Note: Apple hardware repairs not available.</p>
          <span class="learn-more">Learn about screen repair →</span>
        </a>
        <a id="virus-removal" href="/services/virus-removal" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Virus & Malware Removal</h3>
          <p>Thorough cleaning and protection setup to get your computer running safely again.</p>
          <span class="learn-more">Learn about virus removal →</span>
        </a>
        <a id="data-recovery" href="/services/data-recovery" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><ellipse cx="12" cy="12" rx="10" ry="3"/><path d="M2 12c0 1.66 4.48 3 10 3s10-1.34 10-3"/><path d="M2 12v6c0 1.66 4.48 3 10 3s10-1.34 10-3v-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Data Recovery</h3>
          <p>Lost important files? I use professional recovery software to retrieve deleted, corrupted or lost data from drives, USB drives and memory cards.</p>
          <span class="learn-more">Learn about data recovery →</span>
        </a>
        <a id="hardware-upgrades" href="/services/hardware-upgrades" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="2" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="2" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="22"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="22"/><line x1="2" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="2" y1="15" x2="4" y2="15"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="22" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="15" x2="22" y2="15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Hardware Upgrades</h3>
          <p>Speed up your machine with RAM upgrades, SSD installations, and other hardware improvements. Windows and Linux machines only.</p>
          <span class="learn-more">Learn about hardware upgrades →</span>
        </a>
        <a id="broken-tech-repairs" href="/services/broken-tech-repairs" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Broken Tech Repairs</h3>
          <p>Physically damaged or completely dead devices? I diagnose and fix a wide range of broken tech issues.</p>
          <span class="learn-more">Learn about broken tech repairs →</span>
        </a>
        <a id="gaming-console-repair" href="/services/gaming-console-repair" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M6 12h.01M10 12h.01M7 9l-1 3 1 3M13 9l1 3-1 3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Gaming Console Repair</h3>
          <p>PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch and more. I diagnose and repair common console issues including disc drives, overheating and more.</p>
          <span class="learn-more">Learn about gaming console repair →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Web Design Spotlight -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af,#2563eb);padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="web-spotlight-inner">
        <div>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#93c5fd;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Also Available</p>
          <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:white;margin-bottom:0.75rem;line-height:1.2;">Professional Website Design & Management</h2>
          <p style="color:#bfdbfe;line-height:1.75;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">I don't just fix tech. I build it too. Fast, modern, mobile-friendly websites for small businesses across the North Country. You own it outright. No monthly Squarespace fees, no bloated WordPress plugins.</p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
            <span class="web-badge">100/100 Lighthouse</span>
            <span class="web-badge">10/10 WAVE</span>
            <span class="web-badge">WCAG AA Accessible</span>
            <span class="web-badge">You Own It Outright</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;">
            <a href="/web-services" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:white;color:#1e40af;font-weight:700;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.95rem;">
              View Packages & Pricing
              <svg style="height:1rem;width:1rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/why-different" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);color:white;font-weight:600;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.95rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">
              Why My Sites Are Different
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="web-price-cards">
          <div class="web-price-card">
            <div class="web-price-label">Starter</div>
            <div class="web-price-amount">$750</div>
            <div class="web-price-desc">1-3 pages</div>
          </div>
          <div class="web-price-card web-price-featured">
            <div style="font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;color:#2563eb;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.1rem;">Most Popular</div>
            <div class="web-price-label">Professional</div>
            <div class="web-price-amount">$2,000</div>
            <div class="web-price-desc">5-15 pages</div>
          </div>
          <div class="web-price-card">
            <div class="web-price-label">Premium</div>
            <div class="web-price-amount">$3,500+</div>
            <div class="web-price-desc">30+ pages</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Software & OS -->
  <section style="background:white;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">Software & OS</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.25rem;">Operating Systems & Remote Help</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.6;">OS installs, software troubleshooting and remote support across all major platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="software-layout">
        <div class="services-grid-two">
          <a id="mac-software" href="/services/mac-software" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/><path d="M7 8h.01M12 8h.01"/><circle cx="17" cy="8" r="1"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Mac & Apple Software</h3>
            <p>macOS installation, upgrades and troubleshooting on any Mac. I also install Linux on older Macs (2012 to 2018) to give them a new life. Software only.</p>
            <span class="learn-more">Learn about Mac & Apple software →</span>
          </a>
          <a id="remote-support" href="/services/remote-support" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Remote Support</h3>
            <p>Can't make it in? I can diagnose and fix many software issues remotely. Fast, convenient support from the comfort of your own home.</p>
            <span class="learn-more">Learn about remote support →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="platform-panel">
          <p style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;margin-bottom:1rem;">Platforms I Support</p>
          <div class="platform-list">
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">Windows</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">Full support, all versions</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/><path d="M7 8h.01M12 8h.01"/><circle cx="17" cy="8" r="1"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">macOS</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">Software only, no hardware</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="2" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="2" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="22"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="22"/><line x1="2" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="2" y1="15" x2="4" y2="15"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="22" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="15" x2="22" y2="15"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">Linux</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">All major distros</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">ChromeOS</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">Chromebook support</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">Android</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">Software & malware removal</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Support & Learning -->
  <section style="background:#f8fafc;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">Support & Learning</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.25rem;">On-Site Help & Tech Tutoring</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.6;">In person or remote help for anyone who wants to get more comfortable with their technology.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="software-layout">
        <div class="services-grid-two">
          <a id="on-site-tech-support" href="/services/on-site-tech-support" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>On-Site Tech Support</h3>
            <p>I come to you! From WiFi setup to teaching you how to use your devices safely, I offer friendly on-site visits for homes and small businesses in the Littleton area.</p>
            <span class="learn-more">Learn about on-site tech support →</span>
          </a>
          <a id="tech-tutoring" href="/services/tech-tutoring" class="service-card" style="text-decoration:none;display:block;">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Tech Tutoring</h3>
            <p>Patient, friendly one-on-one tech help for all skill levels. Email, safe browsing, device setup, and anything else you need help understanding.</p>
            <span class="learn-more">Learn about tech tutoring →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="platform-panel">
          <p style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;margin-bottom:1rem;">What to Expect</p>
          <div class="platform-list">
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">I Come to You</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">On-site visits in the Littleton area</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">Remote Available</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">Video call sessions from anywhere</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">$50 to $65/hr</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">30 minute minimum for tutoring</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">Ages 18+</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">Any skill level welcome</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="platform-item">
              <div class="platform-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M8 9a4 4 0 1 1 4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="platform-name">No Question Too Basic</div>
                <div class="platform-desc">Friendly, judgment-free help</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af,#2563eb);padding:4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:40rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:white;margin-bottom:1rem;">Don't See What You Need?</h2>
      <p style="color:#bfdbfe;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2rem;">Just ask. Describe what's going on and I'll let you know what I can do.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:1rem;">
        <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:white;color:#2563eb;font-weight:700;padding:0.875rem 2rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;">
          <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          Get in Touch
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+18022341552" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);color:white;font-weight:600;padding:0.875rem 2rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">
          <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.28h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.96a16 16 0 0 0 6.29 6.29l.54-.54a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21.28 17z"/></svg>
          (802) 234-1552
        </a>
      </div>
      <p style="color:#93c5fd;font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">Android phone screen repair coming later in 2026.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .services-grid { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  .software-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 2rem; align-items: start; }
  .services-grid-two { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  .platform-panel { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; min-width: 220px; }
  .platform-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.875rem; }
  .platform-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .platform-icon { display: flex; height: 2.25rem; width: 2.25rem; min-width: 2.25rem; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 0.375rem; background: #dbeafe; color: #2563eb; }
